(1, 'Austin Public Library', '710 W Cesar Chavez St, Austin, TX 78701, United States', 'https://www.google.com/maps?q=710+W+Cesar+Chavez+St+Austin+Tx+78701', 'Head west on W 24th St towards Guadalupe St. Turn left onto Guadalupe St. Pass by University Co-op. Turn right. Turn left onto Nueces St. Turn right onto W 2nd St/W Willie Nelson Blvd.'),
(2, 'Bruno-Lösche-Bibliothek', 'Perleberger Str. 33, 10559 Berlin', 'https://www.openstreetmap.org/search?query=Perleberger%20Str.%2033%2C%2010559%20Berlin', 'Take the U9 to Birkenstraße. Walk toward the large street, Stromstraße, cross the intersection and continue on until Perleberger Str. Turn left The library is on the left.');
